10) What's AC? Why does it matter?

Armour class or AC for short, is your armour defense rating.  The better your AC rating, the harder you are to be hit.  There is also no way for you to know your armor class, and this is quite intentional.

11) What is alignment?

Alignment is the basic attitude of your character towards morality and laws.  To find out more about a specific alignment, type : <help ALIGNMENT NAME>.  The characters alignment is a major factor in determining how you will roleplay your character.

14) I have an idea for something new here, who do I tell?
 
Just type <game idea SHORT DESCRIPTION>. You'll enter editor that will post to board visible only to immortals so they'll able to evaluate your idea.

